==English==

===Noun===
'''chironomid'''  (''plural:'' '''[[chironomids]]''')


# informal name for the non-biting [[midges]] or [[Chironomidae]], a family of true flies ([[Diptera]])
#:''Fossil chironomids have proven useful as indicators of climatic change.''

